{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I was born in Switzerland"},{"time":4000,"text":"and raised in Ghana, West Africa."},{"time":7000,"text":"Ghana felt safe to me as a child."},{"time":9000,"text":"I was free, I was happy."},{"time":13000,"text":"The early 70s"},{"time":15000,"text":"marked a time of musical and artistic excellence in Ghana."},{"time":18000,"text":"But then by the end of the decade,"},{"time":20000,"text":"the country had fallen back into political instability"},{"time":23000,"text":"and mismanagement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":27000,"text":"In 1979,"},{"time":29000,"text":"I witnessed my first military coup."},{"time":33000,"text":"We the children had gathered at a friend's house."},{"time":36000,"text":"It was a dimly lit shack."},{"time":38000,"text":"There was a beaten up black and white television"},{"time":40000,"text":"flickering in the background,"},{"time":43000,"text":"and a former head of state and general"},{"time":45000,"text":"was being blindfolded"},{"time":47000,"text":"and tied to the pole."},{"time":49000,"text":"The firing squad aimed, fired --"},{"time":52000,"text":"the general was dead."},{"time":54000,"text":"Now this was being broadcast live."},{"time":57000,"text":"And shortly after, we left the country,"},{"time":60000,"text":"and we returned to Switzerland."}]},{"cues":[{"time":62000,"text":"Now Europe came as a shock to me,"},{"time":65000,"text":"and I think I started feeling the need"},{"time":68000,"text":"to shed my skin in order to fit in."},{"time":71000,"text":"I wanted to blend in like a chameleon."},{"time":73000,"text":"I think it was a tactic of survival."},{"time":76000,"text":"And it worked, or so I believed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79000,"text":"So here I was in 2008"},{"time":84000,"text":"wondering where I was in my life."},{"time":87000,"text":"And I felt I was being typecast as an actor."},{"time":90000,"text":"I was always playing the exotic African."},{"time":93000,"text":"I was playing the violent African,"},{"time":95000,"text":"the African terrorist."},{"time":97000,"text":"And I was thinking,"},{"time":99000,"text":"how many terrorists could I possibly play"},{"time":101000,"text":"before turning into one myself?"},{"time":104000,"text":"And I had become ashamed of the other,"},{"time":107000,"text":"the African in me."},{"time":110000,"text":"And fortunately I decided in 2008"},{"time":113000,"text":"to return to Ghana,"},{"time":115000,"text":"after 28 years of absence."},{"time":118000,"text":"I wanted to document on film"},{"time":120000,"text":"the 2008 presidential elections."},{"time":123000,"text":"And there, I started by searching"},{"time":126000,"text":"for the footprints in my childhood."},{"time":128000,"text":"And before I even knew it,"},{"time":130000,"text":"I was suddenly on a stage"},{"time":132000,"text":"surrounded by thousands of cheering people"},{"time":134000,"text":"during a political rally."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136000,"text":"And I realized that, when I'd left the country,"},{"time":139000,"text":"free and fair elections in a democratic environment"},{"time":142000,"text":"were a dream."},{"time":144000,"text":"And now that I'd returned, that dream had become reality,"},{"time":147000,"text":"though a fragile reality."},{"time":149000,"text":"And I was thinking,"},{"time":151000,"text":"was Ghana searching for its identity"},{"time":153000,"text":"like I was looking for my identity?"},{"time":155000,"text":"Was what was happening in Ghana a metaphor"},{"time":157000,"text":"for what was happening in me?"},{"time":161000,"text":"And it was as if through the standards of my Western life,"},{"time":167000,"text":"I hadn't lived up to my full potential."},{"time":170000,"text":"I mean, nor had Ghana,"},{"time":172000,"text":"even though we had been trying very hard."}]},{"cues":[{"time":174000,"text":"Now in 1957,"},{"time":176000,"text":"Ghana was the first sub-Saharan country"},{"time":178000,"text":"to gain its independence."},{"time":180000,"text":"In the late 50s,"},{"time":182000,"text":"Ghana and Singapore had the same GDP."},{"time":185000,"text":"I mean, today, Singapore is a First World country"},{"time":188000,"text":"and Ghana is not."},{"time":191000,"text":"But maybe it was time to prove to myself,"},{"time":194000,"text":"yes, it's important to understand the past,"},{"time":196000,"text":"it is important to look at it in a different light,"},{"time":200000,"text":"but maybe we should look at the strengths in our own culture"},{"time":204000,"text":"and build on those foundations in the present."}]},{"cues":[{"time":208000,"text":"So here I was, December 7th, 2008."},{"time":213000,"text":"The polling stations opened to the voters at 7:00 AM,"},{"time":218000,"text":"but voters, eager to take their own political fate into their hands,"},{"time":222000,"text":"were starting to line up at 4:00 AM in the morning."},{"time":225000,"text":"And they had traveled from near, they had traveled from far,"},{"time":228000,"text":"because they wanted to make their voices heard."},{"time":230000,"text":"And I asked one of the voters, I said, \"Whom are you going to vote for?\""},{"time":233000,"text":"And he said, \"I'm sorry, I can't tell you.\""},{"time":236000,"text":"He said that his vote was in his heart."},{"time":239000,"text":"And I understood, this was their election,"},{"time":242000,"text":"and they weren't going to let anyone"},{"time":244000,"text":"take it away from them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246000,"text":"Now the first round of the voting didn't bring forth a clear winner --"},{"time":249000,"text":"so nobody had achieved the absolute majority --"},{"time":253000,"text":"so voting went into a second round three weeks later."},{"time":256000,"text":"The candidates were back on the road; they were campaigning."},{"time":259000,"text":"The rhetoric of the candidates, of course, changed."},{"time":261000,"text":"The heat was on."},{"time":263000,"text":"And then the cliche came to haunt us."},{"time":268000,"text":"There were claims of intimidation"},{"time":270000,"text":"at the polling stations,"},{"time":272000,"text":"of ballot boxes being stolen."},{"time":276000,"text":"Inflated results started coming in"},{"time":279000,"text":"and the mob was starting to get out of control."},{"time":282000,"text":"We witnessed the eruption of violence in the streets."},{"time":286000,"text":"People were being beaten brutally."},{"time":289000,"text":"The army started firing their guns. People were scrambling."},{"time":292000,"text":"It was complete chaos."},{"time":294000,"text":"And my heart sank,"},{"time":296000,"text":"because I thought, here we are again."},{"time":298000,"text":"Here is another proof"},{"time":300000,"text":"that the African is not capable of governing himself."},{"time":303000,"text":"And not only that, I am documenting it --"},{"time":306000,"text":"documenting my own cultural shortcomings."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310000,"text":"So when the echo of the gunshots"},{"time":313000,"text":"had lingered,"},{"time":315000,"text":"it was soon drowned by the chanting of the mob,"},{"time":317000,"text":"and I didn't believe what I was hearing."},{"time":319000,"text":"They were chanting, \"We want peace."},{"time":321000,"text":"We want peace.\""},{"time":324000,"text":"And I realized it had to come from the people."},{"time":327000,"text":"After all, they decide,"},{"time":329000,"text":"and they did."},{"time":331000,"text":"So the sounds that were before distorted and loud,"},{"time":335000,"text":"were suddenly a melody."},{"time":338000,"text":"The sounds of the voices were harmonious."},{"time":341000,"text":"So it could happen."},{"time":344000,"text":"A democracy could be upheld peacefully."},{"time":347000,"text":"It could be, by the will of the masses"},{"time":350000,"text":"who were now urgently pressing"},{"time":352000,"text":"with all their heart and all their will"},{"time":354000,"text":"for peace."}]},{"cues":[{"time":356000,"text":"Now here's an interesting comparison."},{"time":359000,"text":"We in the West,"},{"time":361000,"text":"we preach the values,"},{"time":363000,"text":"the golden light of democracy,"},{"time":366000,"text":"that we are the shining example of how it's done."},{"time":369000,"text":"But when it comes down to it,"},{"time":372000,"text":"Ghana found itself in the same place"},{"time":376000,"text":"in which the U.S. election stalled"},{"time":378000,"text":"in the 2000 presidential elections --"},{"time":380000,"text":"Bush versus Gore."},{"time":383000,"text":"But instead of the unwillingness of the candidates"},{"time":386000,"text":"to allow the system to proceed and the people to decide,"},{"time":389000,"text":"Ghana honored democracy"},{"time":392000,"text":"and its people."},{"time":394000,"text":"It didn't leave it up to the Supreme Court to decide;"},{"time":397000,"text":"the people did."}]},{"cues":[{"time":400000,"text":"Now the second round of voting"},{"time":403000,"text":"did not bring forth a clear winner either."},{"time":405000,"text":"I mean, it was so incredibly close."},{"time":407000,"text":"The electoral commissioner declared,"},{"time":410000,"text":"with the consent of the parties,"},{"time":412000,"text":"to run an unprecedented"},{"time":414000,"text":"second re-run."},{"time":416000,"text":"So the people went back to the polls"},{"time":420000,"text":"to determine their own president,"},{"time":422000,"text":"not the legal system."},{"time":424000,"text":"And guess what, it worked."},{"time":428000,"text":"The defeated candidate"},{"time":430000,"text":"gave up power"},{"time":432000,"text":"and made way for Ghana to move into a new democratic cycle."},{"time":435000,"text":"I mean, at the absolute time"},{"time":437000,"text":"for the absolute need of democracy,"},{"time":439000,"text":"they did not abuse their power."},{"time":444000,"text":"The belief in true democracy and in the people runs deep,"},{"time":448000,"text":"proving that the African is capable of governing himself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":453000,"text":"Now the uphill battle for Ghana and for Africa"},{"time":456000,"text":"is not over,"},{"time":458000,"text":"but I have proof that the other side of democracy exists,"},{"time":462000,"text":"and that we must not take it for granted."},{"time":465000,"text":"Now I have learned"},{"time":467000,"text":"that my place is not just in the West or in Africa,"},{"time":471000,"text":"and I'm still searching"},{"time":473000,"text":"for my identity,"},{"time":475000,"text":"but I saw Ghana"},{"time":478000,"text":"create democracy better."},{"time":480000,"text":"Ghana taught me"},{"time":482000,"text":"to look at people differently"},{"time":484000,"text":"and to look at myself differently."},{"time":487000,"text":"And yes,"},{"time":489000,"text":"we Africans can."}]},{"cues":[{"time":491000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":493000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}